{"tid":649094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IS阿富汗炸彈人扮採訪自爆　25死9記者殉職","createTime":"2018-05-01T09:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T13:42:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a18624bd9cadcf362f7d1ba556ea918e5e6bd6c4","tid":649094,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:02:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180501/20377861?_ga=2.82503446.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20377861%3F_ga%3D2.82503446.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=gCz%2Bn9pUQ%2BW1BqbAcjAdycn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9349cd0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180501%2F20377861%3F_ga%3D2.82503446.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=15b55abd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180501/20377861?_ga=2.82503446.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月01日 <br />\n<br />\nIS阿富汗炸彈人扮採訪自爆　25死9記者殉職<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180501/large/a1103a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180501%2Flarge%2Fa1103a.gif&h=7e4662a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■第二名人肉彈爆炸，令多名記者倒地，警員急忙施救。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿富汗喀布爾（Kabul）昨日發生針對傳媒的連環自殺式炸彈襲擊，釀成至少25死49傷，當中包括1名法新社記者及8名其他記者，極端組織「伊斯蘭國」（IS）承認施襲。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180501/large/a1103b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180501%2Flarge%2Fa1103b.gif&h=f0c96547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法新社殉職攝記馬拉伊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法新社首席攝記遇害<br />\n<br />\n警方指，喀布爾首宗爆炸後數分鐘，即發生第二宗襲擊，「炸彈人偽裝成記者，在人群中引爆炸彈」，在場採訪的法新社首席攝記馬拉伊（Shah Marai）被炸死，其餘遇害的包括至少4名阿富汗傳媒記者，以及多名自由歐洲電台當地記者。遇難者亦包括4名警員。<br />\n<br />\nIS在聲明中，稱「當異教徒的安全部隊、傳媒等人趕到現場行動時，一名兄弟引爆炸彈背心自我犧牲，出奇不意地取他們的命」。馬拉伊1996年當上法新社司機，後來成為全職攝記，法新社指他拍攝阿富汗的悲慘衝突超過15年，讚揚他「擁有超凡力量、勇氣及氣量」。<br />\n<br />\n另邊廂，南部達曼（Daman）一間清真寺附近亦發生相信由塔利班發動自殺式炸彈襲擊，炸彈人在外國軍隊汽車途經時引爆汽車炸彈，11名兒童罹難，另外17名平民、警員及羅馬尼亞士兵受傷。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/德新社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n保守黨明日之星　難敵「政治墳墓」宿命<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n美關稅豁免到期　英法德表明企硬"},{"pid":"bff738e5e11f3ef239d838b363c4d7f58e42cb9a","tid":649094,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"侵侵消滅左IS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ee6efca4bd6bb7df3d09e3c9bdfee4b146770e","tid":649094,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:29:21.000Z","msg":"Daesh竟然仲未死晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639850882b24d351d7bebdeed91d35323b07dae2","tid":649094,"uid":3457,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:33:10.000Z","msg":"香港都準備有清真寺🕌️<br />\n到香港了"},{"pid":"d6fb13a8b579a2a32f963505ef699873e9d928e2","tid":649094,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:40:04.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"1408ef23276f5eb6a26427dfcd1e7befcb8758f8","tid":649094,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T09:41:19.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"8626b6148ee2233aa55d3202d5f7ac9a0d9b5dea","tid":649094,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c10b82d5e8b0e0a2a7c2caaaec38e2d7cce1d88","tid":649094,"uid":104443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bff738e5e11f3ef239d838b363c4d7f58e42cb9a","tid":649094,"uid":